description: This Chainlink VRF top 15% score Gaston purrs with a rating of 26, and a multiplier of 5x. It has a total score of 130, and confers the same amount of votes in the EtherCats DAO. The card game properties are Box for North, Stringalong for East, Leverage for South, and Stringalong for West. Gaston has the personality suit of whale. A rendering of the card can be found at https://cards.ethercats.eth.link/60265-47670-3.html. Each Founders Series cat is part of NFT history. These fine felines represent the first verifiably random NFTs minted with Chainlink VRF.
name: Gaston [130 Votes, Top 15% Score]
